and all the police officers killed, except Inspector Lindsay Denton, who organized the operation 
at very short notice and who only informed DCC Dryden of the route. 
Ted Hastings asks Steve and Kate to interview her but Kate pulls out, claiming one of the dead officers, 
Jayne Akers, was a friend although she has been having an affair with Jayne's husband Rich
